						 <p>Me, personally? I see it a different way.<br /> Look at the Containment Procedures.<br /> Then, look at the creature's message<br /> Then, look at the Procedures again.<br /> &quot;feed&quot;<br /> Here's a question: does this thing really want more trash?</p> 
